All the data presented here were medians and range (minimum-maximum). 
WBC: white blood cell; PLT: platelet; ALT: alanine aminotransferase; AST: aspartate aminotransferase; GGT, gamma-glutamyl transferase; Tbil, total bilirubin; 
Dbil, direct bilirubin; LDH, lactic dehydrogenase; CK, creatine kinase.

